ygData.messageBody:
Made the following updates to my site:

Changed the name of the home page to EverQuest.htm, please change your
bookmarks (if you have it bookmarked).

http://www.dubuque.net/~sirkal/EverQuest.htm

Added Qeynos Hills.

Added Blackburrow, Surface.


Due to the fact that my website is updated so infrequently, I have created
this e-mail list to keep interested parties informed of updates.
If you do not wish to be part of this list please just e-mail me saying so
and you will be removed.

Xezol - Lvl 10 Gnome Mag on E'Ci
